		<h3>Video Tutorials</h3>
		<br/>

		<p>So far a number of video tutorials are available. You can run them your self executing the following commands:</p>

		<code>snowmix ini/text_tutorials.ini</code>

		<p>and then in second window</p>

		<code>output2screen</code>

		<p>and then in third window (although not strictly needed)</p>

		<code>input2feed 4 4</code>

